pageTitle: City Center 30286 Thomaston, GA Neighborhood Profile
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {10528=Real estate in the City Center of Thomaston, GA is primarily made up of small (studio to two bedroom) to medium sized (three or four bedroom) single-family homes and small apartment buildings. Most of the residential real estate is occupied by a mixture of owners and renters. Many of the residences in the City Center neighborhood are established but not old, having been built between 1970 and 1999. A number of residences were also built before 1940.}
